1. Create a directory for the sketch
2. Copy the Makefile.template into the sketch directory
3. Add function prototypes if required
4. Add any libraries to the Makefile
	ARDUINO_LIBS = ros_lib Wire
5. Update the target board
	ARDUINO_PORT = /dev/ttyUSB_IMU
6. Run "make to build the sketch
7. Run "make clean" to clear the build directories
8. Run "make upload" to upload the sketch
9. Run "make upload monitor clean" to build the sketch, upload it, opsn a "screen" Serial monitor and cllean down the build directories
